This uses the toplevel configure.ac
This uses the toplevel Makefile.am via SUBDIRS

API.md describes the API.  Some of it is not stable, and intended to be
replaced soon with scripts that implement a more stable API.  Those are only
described in the source code.

For OpenWRT ("SIMETBox") builds, refer to the openwrt feed, it has a higher
level ubus RPC API that should be used, and its implementation can shed light
on the current inner workings of the SIMET measurement engine.
